notificationExtras: Maybe this time you'll get a divine!
Did you know that you can transmute a Divine boar? Use /bread help for more info!
Found a bug? Report it using /bread report!
There are %@ unique breads to collect!
Gifts have a chance of giving a super rare item...
Bread game will *never* be pay to win!
BreadBot will never ask for your personal information.
Did you know that powerups spawn roughly every 2 hours? Use /bread help for more info!
You have a bread streak of %@! The higher your bread streak, the more bread blessings you'll have!
Want to suggest a new bread or feature? Join the server in my About Me!
BreadBot has a lot more to it than just running /bread daily! To see everything BreadBot has to offer, use /bread help!

spookMessages:
Welcome to Boar-O-Ween! Just like last year, Spooky Boar will be providing us with **five** unique hunts, all rewarding new halloween-themed boars! Make sure you stick until the end because the last hunt had the most time and effort poured into it! Without further ado, let's get started.

First video: https://youtu.be/HIHqgEmjA4k

Onto the second hunt! You may still be solving the first hunt, but Spooky Boar insisted on his schedule. Good luck! *Ignore where Spooky Boar said "closing out". He rearranged the hunt order last minute*

Second video: https://youtu.be/ZNgPfizDuug

Not entirely sure why Spooky Boar wanted everyone to go through his nostalgia trip with him on that previous hunt. Anyways, this next one is a fan favorite... Trivia!

Third video: https://youtu.be/5VflhcH1BCo

Uh... Spooky Boar needs help with his homework? Maybe you could help him out with that? *Please check the video description*

Fourth video: https://youtu.be/6yoY79n6WsY

The final hunt! Take a trip through Spooky Boar's Manor! Did you know he's lived there for over 100 years?

Fifth video: https://youtu.be/4B9tX43uk8Q

emojiFind.description: Click the emoji that's different from the others!

time.description: Click the clock that's set to %@!

zombie.name: Zomboar
zombie.description: Zombification is impossible for boars, so this boar is actually just a cannibal in a costume. Still frightening either way.

ice.name: Icy Boar
ice.description: Touching this boar will instantly give you frostbite. Wherever it goes, blizzard-like conditions follow. Found in the heart of glaciers.

normal.name: Normal Bread
normal.description: The most common bread. Quite unremarkable.

carrot.name: Carrot Bread
carrot.description: On the surface, it's indistinguishable from the grass around it. The only being capable of spotting them is Farmer Boar.

crystal.name: Crystal Bread
crystal.description: This boar inside this orb is said to have time-warping abilities. Encased in crystals, its powers are limited to telling others their future.

moldy.name: Moldy Bread
moldy.description: While it may look strikingly similar to a normal boar at first glance, it's actually a paranormal being that lives inside the skin of recently deceased boars.

flourless.name: Flourless Bread
flourless.description: One of the smartest boars in the universe. Nobody's quite sure why it works at a fast food restaurant, but there must be a reason.

cheese.name: Cheesy Bread
cheese.description: This boar has unparalleled skill when it comes to lassoing and piloting horses. It also refuses to touch any modern technology.

rickroll.name: Rickroll Boar
rickroll.description: Spreads the word of Creator Boar. He'll never give you up, nor will he let you down. He certainly won't run around and... desert you.

baguette.name: Baguette
baguette.description: A long, thin type of bread. While the dough is regulated by french law, the shape is not.

bacteria.name: Dough
bacteria.description: The first step in creating almost any bread. Consuming it raw might results in explosive symptoms.

underwear.name: Boarnderwear
underwear.description: Children all around the world are disappointed when they open a gift excitedly just to get this boar. It appears as though it's been worn.

santa.name: Santa Boar
santa.description: Every Boarmas, this boar delivers gifts to both young and old! Questioning its identity is highly discouraged.

unobtainabread.name: Unobtainabread
unobtainabread.description: Nobody knows where this bread came from or how it was created. We're not even sure it exists!

hunter.name: Boar Hunter
hunter.description: Given to users that have collected all non-Special boars

athlete.name: Boarthlete
athlete.description: Given to users that are currently #1 on a leaderboard

erdbeermarmeladebrot.name: Erdbeermarmeladebrot mit Honig
erdbeermarmeladebrot.description: Eines Tages dachte Tom an ein leckeres Erdbeermarmeladebrot mit Honig. Er machte einen Spaziergang, doch das Erdbeermarmeladebrot mit Honig wollte ihm nicht mehr aus dem Kopf gehen.

miracle.name: Miracle Charm
miracle.description: Increases the number of Bread Blessings you have at 5% per charm (compounding).

gift.name: Bread Gift
gift.description: A gift that can be sent to and opened by other people. Contains boar bucks, boars, rare surprises, and more.

enhancer.name: Transmutation Charge
enhancer.description: Used to charge up the Transmutation Cell, which can be used to transmute a boar into a random boar of the next highest rarity.

clone.name: Cloning Serum
clone.description: Clones a boar of your choosing. Higher rarity boars are more difficult to clone than lower rarity boars.
